Dependencies
============

You'll need the following Python dependencies installed, most can be easily
installed with pip (or easy_install, if you must):

* elasticsearch - for connecting to your ElasticSearch cluster
* bottle - for HTTP request routing and handling
* dateutil - for timestamp mangling (try your distro packages)
* pyScss - for CSS preprocessing in Makefile (pip or distro)
* WSGI app container (optional)
